videoDetails.Title: The Worst War Thunder Challenge
videoDetails.Description:
Decal link: https://tinyurl.com/42thwzv3

After playing War Thunder for years, you have to start challenging yourself in unique ways. Someone asked if I could use a tank with a dozer blade to only engage targets from trenches. I thought the Strv 103 would be perfect for that.

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.
